h off nicely on that occasion. Now out to the mile which looks a big tick and he looks a nice horse on the rise. Can get back to his best this. 11. RISING PHOENIX improved last time out when out to this track and trip. He draws better this time around with Badel hopping on board and he's found some form lately. Drawn ideally and can be in the finish again. 2. PRESTIGE GOOD comes back in grade today after jumping favourite in stronger company last time out. Looks well placed back in grade and won't be far away.\",\"runners\":[4,7,11,2],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Tom Wood","tipRunnerNumbers":[4,5,7,10]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,2,7,4]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,9,2,12]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[4,1,7,2]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,7,5,4]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,2,5,10]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[3,4,7,10]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[7,3,2,4]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"RunningDouble","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quaddie","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":8,"venueMnemonic":"SHA","raceType":"R"}}]}}}